HEADWORD: Greenbacker
<hw>Green"back"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of those who
supported greenback or paper money, and opposed the resumption of specie
payments.</def> <mark>[Colloq. U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

